ike":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇都4年難追D喎 ching</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n難追係因為太遲意識到問題<br />\n下下去到final year先去諗追hon梗係難<br />\n一向都話越遲追越難追<br />\n追hon應該係year 1完既時候(或之前)就要考慮<br />\n更何況難=不可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就視乎個hon對閣下既價值<br />\n有冇追既意義<br />\n事在人為, 要追無話唔可能<br />\n<br />\n對我而言<br />\n追hon一黎對得住家人<br />\n二黎係想挑戰自己 (主要係呢個意義逼我追hon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n三黎比條後路自己行 (摶入mphil/master/靚job offer)<br />\n<br />\n追hon係一個<span style=\"color: red;\">認清事實後既行動</span>, 而唔係一個口號<br />\n而事實=每個sem既GPA<br />\n過三爆四唔係開sem前既口號, 而係出GPA後俾自己既承諾<br />\n有承諾先會有計劃點追 (retake摶靚grade/reg靚grade科/搵大神carry/自己搵方法讀好佢)"},{"pid":"e8fe3a2e4a49900fcfe7c9b83f4823d725cc755d","tid":568752,"uid":54875,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"從來沒有<br />\n連登仔咁勁 一個唔留神就first hon啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你倒追2nd up?"},{"pid":"acf10e978256790a7a3644d2fd40873dfa00dc58","tid":568752,"uid":110719,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6f1b1230478a65cf25df940c2046b43a79e82354","tid":568752,"uid":73010,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇都4年難追D喎 ching</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n難追係因為太遲意識到問題<br />\n下下去到final year先去諗追hon梗係難<br />\n一向都話越遲追越難追<br />\n追hon應該係year 1完既時候(或之前)就要考慮<br />\n更何況難=不可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就視乎個hon對閣下既價值<br />\n有冇追既意義<br />\n事在人為, 要追無話唔可能<br />\n<br />\n對我而言<br />\n追hon一黎對得住家人<br />\n二黎係想挑戰自己 (主要係呢個意義逼我追hon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n三黎比條後路自己行 (摶入mphil/master/靚job offer)<br />\n<br />\n追hon係一個<span style=\"color: red;\">認清事實後既行動</span>, 而唔係一個口號<br />\n而事實=每個sem既GPA<br />\n過三爆四唔係開sem前既口號, 而係出GPA後俾自己既承諾<br />\n有承諾先會有計劃點追 (retake摶靚grade/reg靚grade科/搵大神carry/自己搵方法讀好佢)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:26:01.000Z","msg":"咁考好dse唔係計劃? 點解要讀ive上大學?"},{"pid":"7d2d0b16ca29fb36ea9f3e574c1ec0f3e2cca1fd","tid":568752,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:31:52.000Z","msg":"Ive世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a0f05beb3370d8eb166066013c16c11e6ef4b8","tid":568752,"uid":73010,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁考好dse唔係計劃? 點解要讀ive上大學?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n考好DSE當然唔係計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係<span style=\"color: red;\">方法</span><br />\n而你<span style=\"color: red;\">計劃</span>既目標係<span style=\"color: red;\">上大學</span><br />\n而上大學唔係得一種方法<br />\n<br />\n經其他方式入U有好多原因<br />\n可以係每個人都有個人適合既學習方式<br />\nDSE套填鴨式system唔啱你就只可以搵其他方法上大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦可以係ive學費平D, 經IVE入U overall 4年可以慳返兩皮(前提你好有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n而家講緊係讀U個張cert (一張可能係你人生最後既一張成績表)<br />\n正如你見工唔會拎小學張grad cert出黎講<br />\n呢張成績表有可能影響人地點睇你個人既入場卷 (當然視乎你個行既老細在唔在意hon)"},{"pid":"7c10fe32427e862adc4ed2fa906855fa76ebae7b","tid":568752,"uid":80397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:28:25.000Z","msg":"year 1 sem 1: 2.5x --&gt; year 4 sem 2: 3.9x <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時盡左力但個grade無想像中咁好 <br />\n有時諗住hea 讀 個grade出到黎反而靚<br />\n勤力(交齊assignment + 熟悉course content) 同埋運氣 (reg岩科+ prof睇你順眼) 都好重要<br />\n摸索左3年先識"},{"pid":"5b2b4606ab69d6bc23f81fd6899d55d147dfaf82","tid":568752,"uid":126831,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c10fe32427e862adc4ed2fa906855fa76ebae7b","tid":568752,"uid":80397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:28:25.000Z","msg":"